OL,3,CInfected blood victim says government
OL,4,C'dragging feet' over payouts
OL,6,FA man from York who was infected with
OL,7,FHepatitis C in the contaminated blood
OL,8,Fscandal says the government is
OL,9,F"dragging its feet" on compensating
OL,10,Fvictims.
OL,12,FNorman Revill joined others outside
OL,13,FParliament on Wednesday 28 February to
OL,14,Fprotest the lack of progress on
OL,15,Fcompensation while people affected
OL,16,Fcontinue to die.
