OL,3,CInfected blood victim says government
OL,4,C'dragging feet' over payouts
OL,6,FThe scandal has been described as the
OL,7,Fbiggest treatment disaster in NHS
OL,8,Fhistory - with thousands across the UK
OL,9,Finfected with HIV and Hepatitis C
OL,10,Fafter being given blood products in
OL,11,Fthe 1970s and 80s.
OL,13,FMr Revill told ITV Tyne Tees: "I think
OL,14,Fthat it's time now to actually give
OL,15,Feverybody the indication that they're
OL,16,Fgonna get some compensation for this.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
