OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F428A1709237244
OL,3,CInfected blood victim says government
OL,4,C'dragging feet' over payouts
OL,6,F"There's a lot of people here who have
OL,7,Fbeen affected by it but there is a
OL,8,Ftremendous amount of people who aren't
OL,9,Fhere because of the number of people
OL,10,Fwho have died."
OL,12,FMr Revill said he was given two units
OL,13,Fof blood in 1983 following an accident
OL,14,Fand did not realise until eight years
OL,15,Flater that he had contracted Hepatitis
OL,16,FC.
OL,18,FBeing infected with the virus had had
OL,19,Fa "massive" impact on his life, he
OL,20,Fsaid.
