OL,3,CInfected blood victim says government
OL,4,C'dragging feet' over payouts
OL,6,F"Mentally it's been horrendous,"
OL,7,Fcontinued Mr Revill. "The health
OL,8,Fissues that I've experienced. I almost
OL,9,Fgot cirrhosis of the liver. Ive had
OL,10,Ffour liver biopsies.
OL,12,F"(There have been) too numerous
OL,13,F(issues) to mention really. I had 18
OL,14,Fmonths on interferon beta which is
OL,15,Flike a chemotherapy, which is horrific.
OL,17,F"But going through all that, I'm one
OL,18,Fof the lucky ones who have actually
OL,19,Fgot through it all."
