OL,3,CInfected blood victim says government
OL,4,C'dragging feet' over payouts
OL,6,FMr Revill said he had received some
OL,7,Finterim compensation a year ago but it
OL,8,Fwas "not enough to keep my lifestyle
OL,9,Frunning and keep the house running".
OL,11,FIan Lavery, MP for Wansbeck, is a
OL,12,Fmember of the All-Party Parliamentary
OL,13,FGroup (APPG) on Haemophilia and
OL,14,FContaminated Blood.
OL,16,FHe criticised the government for
OL,17,Fdelays in handing giving victims
OL,18,Fjustice and compensation.
