OL,3,CInfected blood victim says government
OL,4,C'dragging feet' over payouts
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Tyne Tees at
OL,7,FWestminster, he said: "Six-hundred-and-
OL,8,Feighty people have died since the
OL,9,Finquiry began and it cannot continue.
OL,11,F"It looks as though this has been
OL,12,Fkicked into the long grass by the
OL,13,Fgovernment, probably trying to limp on
OL,14,Fto get across after the election, and
OL,15,Fthat's not good enough. We need
OL,16,Fjustice for these people and justice
OL,17,Fnow.
