OL,3,CInfected blood victim says government
OL,4,C'dragging feet' over payouts
OL,6,F"These people are dying. The families
OL,7,Fand themselves need justice and they
OL,8,Fneed compensation - without any
OL,9,Ffurther delays."
OL,11,FLast April the chair of the Infected
OL,12,FBlood Inquiry said a full compensation
OL,13,Fscheme - including for the parents and
OL,14,Fchildren of victims - should be set up
OL,15,Fas soon as possible.
OL,17,FThe government's position is to wait
OL,18,Ffor the final report from the public
OL,19,Finquiry - due in May - before setting
OL,20,Fout their approach to full
OL,21,Fcompensation.
