OL,3,CInfected blood victim says government
OL,4,C'dragging feet' over payouts
OL,6,FSpeaking during Prime Minister's
OL,7,FQuestions today, Rishi Sunak said:
OL,8,F"We've consistently acknowledged that
OL,9,Fjustice should be delivered. I gave
OL,10,Fevidence to the public inquiry last
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,F"The government has accepted the moral
OL,14,Fcase for compensation, which is why -
OL,15,Fon Monday, in the other place - we
OL,16,Fcommitted to bringing forward
OL,17,Famendments at report stage of the
OL,18,FVictim and Prisoners Bill, with the
OL,19,Fintention of speeding up the
OL,20,Fimplementation of our response to the
OL,21,FInfected Blood Inquiry."
